{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was nothing you can do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At the beginning, the first day, we felt embarrassed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But after the second, third day, you have to do something, whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the men, they made like holes into the wood of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were, you know, those wagons for animals, as I say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was all made in wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They make little holes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were there in front of everybody-- no privacy, no-- no hygiene, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't wash, or we didn't-- we had no water to drink, never mind to wash.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How many people were in a wagon?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've been telling you, of 70 or 80, at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even they-- even, you know, there was no enough room to be, you know, sitting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One-- many people has to stand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many people have to-- to-- whatever position.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You cannot even turn the other side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because that small area, they cannot fit 80 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was with us at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We still with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- except, you know, I told you, in Rhodes Island, we had given away just the jewelry-- the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they never-- you know, when they took it us-- so the jewelry in Rhodes Island-- when the German before, they took us to barges, they never expected us, I told you, to find so much-- so much precious thing in such a small island.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes, you know, for 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for 10 minutes, you can go in the fields.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the German was looking in case you want, you know, to do your-- your-- you know-- you want to do something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were watching you into the fields next to the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
